<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div>
<p>Special thanks to Clef, TheDeadlyMoose, TroyL, Decibelle, Light and all of the other resurrection authors who helped me with or reviewed this piece. It's the longest I've ever worked on a tale and I'm happy with how it turned out.</p>
<p>Edit: Was reminded by a recent interaction that while I'm pretty sure everyone got the Duke Till Dawn reference I stuck in here, I should mention that's where I got the &quot;kiss your ass goodbye&quot; section from for anyone who hadn't read that tale.</p>
</div>
<hr />
<div id="u-author_block">
